Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE & Knight Frank are pleased to present to the market For Lease 18-22 Lions Park Drive, Yatala. It’s a unique offering, providing first class office and warehouse accommodation in conjunction with the adjoining hardstand area for storage of containers or equipment. The property is located close to the M1 Pacific Motorway on ramp, providing access to Brisbane and Gold Coast markets within 30min. Ideally suited to a contractor, manufacturing business or wholesale/transport operator.   

•	1,857sqm* industrial warehouse on 3,203sqm* of land  
•	Includes adjoining 3,048sqm* of fully fenced/ roadbased hardstand storage
•	485sqm* of well-appointed office over ground and mezzanine levels 
•	1,372sqm* warehouse with dual doors (1x8m* wide sliding door)
•	Wash Bay included onsite 
•	21 car parks         

Please contact the Exclusive Agents, CBRE or Knight Frank for further information or an inspection.

•	Brand new development
•	1,446sqm* freestanding industrial headquarters  
•	199sqm* well-appointed mezzanine office
•	1,247sqm* of 8m (min) high clearspan warehouse
•	2,913sqm* (2,592sqm usable) of ‘Low Impact Industry’ zoned land    
•	3 roller doors access – 2 x 7.5m wide 
•	Dual 9m* crossovers with sliding gate access  
•	Entry point location to Yatala’s most anticipated industrial estate
•	Due for completion May/ June 2022 – Enquire today for early input into design 
•	Contact Exclusive Agents CBRE for more information

CBRE are pleased to present to the market For Lease Lot 103, Homestead Drive, Yatala within Vantage – Yatala. The estate will be home to major users looking to take advantage of being within 30min drive of both Brisbane and the Gold Coast. The estate will have almost direct access onto Exit 38 from the M1 Pacific Motorway as well as internal CCTV, breakout areas and open space park area.     

This is a unique opportunity to locate your business within one of Yatala’s most exclusive business parks.   

Please contact the Exclusive Agents, CBRE for further information.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BRAND NEW HQ – ENTRY POINT LOCATION!

This unique opportunity is situated in the heart of the Yatala Enterprise Area. Ideally located between the two largest consumer markets of Brisbane and the Gold Coast with direct access from the M1 via Exit 38 and Exit 41 in both north and south directions.
